text:
The place is quiet and cool. This place is suitable if used as a place for morning exercise or just a leisurely walk and enjoy the scenery.
There are many chairs provided that can be used to sit and relax and enjoy the natural scenery here.
The place have lots of trees. There are some monkeys that can be seen at the entrance of this place.
It was fine. A bit crowded though.

Beautiful lake and views..long walks, beautiful sceneries and chirping of birds makes your day! Lovely place to visit, chill and relax.. walk trail nicely upgraded and maintained..toilets are clean and sanitized..busy during weekends but manageable and comfortable to walk and explore the placeâ€¦. ðŸ˜Š

A tranquil environment. Great for joggers, walkers, nature lovers. A great natural environment. Need to be alert for moneys (high population) snatching food (somtimes they may become dangerous), snakes (although I did not come across any), insects. A beautiful environment to savour nature.
A visit to the Tree Top is one of the highlights.
